{"tid":471954,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"人生苦短，又係時候行山 (Telegram)","createTime":"2017-11-17T17:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T17:49:14.000Z","uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0f7b9ce3f65cd5df3b29864d325ef3b12409f4","tid":471954,"uid":158199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"又到秋天，各位網友有冇興趣行山下呢?<br />\n我係一個行山新手，平時又唔算多運動，<br />\n原本都唔諗住開Group邀請人行山，<br />\n好驚自己出現又要開Group，但又要唔熟路的情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係慶幸Group內應該至少會有一個行山高手入來join，<br />\n咁就太好了，咁不如開個Group，<br />\n有興趣就入來啦，暫時係public，或者去到５０人就變番private。<br />\n依排天氣唔錯，Group 內或者二至三星期內至少有一次行山活動啦，<br />\n但日後希望至少一至二個月行到一次山啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n注意Group內唔係一個吹水Group，<br />\n有水吹當然唔錯啦，<br />\n但係唔好因為見個Group太靜自己走去quit咗個Group呀。<br />\n有興趣就自己入來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLife is short. You should go hiking.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/lifeisshort_you_should_go_hiking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flifeisshort_you_should_go_hiking&d=9jjekClNMuLH3TYA%2FbvXeP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=271732c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lifeisshort_you_should_go_hiking</a>"},{"pid":"b2928e16067c4b0e886498b2f79b530a4cd7de85","tid":471954,"uid":139139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T17:49:14.000Z","msg":"推一下"}]}